@NODE Introduction "What it actually does..."

	Alerts/Introduction
	===================

  This blanker draws alerts on the screen.

@ENDNODE


@NODE Interface "Configuration preferences..."

	Alerts/Interface
	================

@{b}                Save @{ub}- save and use the current settings.

@{b}                 Use @{ub}- use the current settings.

@{b}                Test @{ub}- test the blanker under the current settings

@{b}              Cancel @{ub}- cancel all changes.


@{b}          Alert Type @{ub}- select what sort of alerts to be drawn.
                       You can choose 1.3, 2.0/3.0.
                       @{i}Default: 2.0/3.0.@{ui}

@{b}         Flash Speed @{ub}- how fast should the border flash.
                       @{i}Default: Medium.@{ui}

@{b}   Duration of Alert @{ub}- how long should the alert remain on screen.
                       @{i}Default: 10 seconds.@{ui}

@{b}Delay Between Alerts @{ub}- the number of seconds to leave the screen
                       blank inbetween displaying the alerts.
                       @{i}Default: 5 seconds.@{ui}

@{b}        Green Alerts @{ub}- allow alerts to come up Green like under
                       kickstart V36.
                       @{i}Default: Off.@{ui}

@{b}    Change Sync Rate @{ub}- currently disabled.
                       @{i}Default: Off.@{ui}


@ENDNODE


